"{\"uid\": \"journal-topics.com-articles-glenview-police-raise-4100-for-illinois-special-olympics-at-cop-on-a-rooftop\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Journal & Topics Media Group | Serving Chicago's Great Northwest Suburbs  Saturday, December 6, 2025  Members of the Glenview Police Department take part in the Cop on a Rooftop fundraiser on May 17.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 199, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo by George LeClaire)  Glenview police took up tactical positions on the roof, in the drive-thru, and in the lobby of the Dunkin Donuts at Lake and Milwaukee avenues on Friday, May 17, raising $4,100 for Illinois Special Olympics.Glenview officers joined officers at nearly two dozen other locations across the Northwest suburbs participating in the Cop on a Rooftop fundraiser.Glenview officers began their watch at Lake and Milwaukee at 5 a.m. May 17, remaining at the scene until about noon.\", \"from\": 200, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 217, \"end\": 225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeClaire_Historic_District\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.907692046804918e-12, \"text\": \"LeClaire\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeClaire_Historic_District\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeClaire_Historic_District\"}, {\"begin\": 228, \"end\": 236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenview_station\", \"score\": 0.9999999989959178, \"rank\": 9.89407572929728e-10, \"text\": \"Glenview\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenview_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenview_station\"}, {\"begin\": 353, \"end\": 362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milwaukee\", \"score\": 0.999999999471811, \"rank\": 5.281537062834797e-10, \"text\": \"Milwaukee\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milwaukee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milwaukee\"}, {\"begin\": 409, \"end\": 417, \"titl